asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

name: Morris "Chip" Moss
description:
Flufs are incorruptible. Or so it was thought. 

Indeed after the holy gathering  at the mythical Great Tree the fluffle was united by the love for each other (and music). But after their emergence from underground and witnessing humankind didn't push everyine towards the right path. There were few who were "inspired" by the greed and hunger for wealth of men. This gave rise to the 'FLUFUZA' whose aim was to take over the Underground first and next Overground. They soon realised that the Great tree held mysteries and treasures capable of helping them attain glory no Fluf or man has ever imagined. 

One of them was Morris Moss. Morris never knew what is family. He unfortunately lost  his parents, both brave soldiers, during 'the wreck'. Growing up he had no home. Orphaned, he would roam around markets trying to  fend for himself. One time while running from the 'Fluf police' he fell from sidewalk  and barely managed to save himself from a speeding Lambo but got himself a chipped ear. From then he was known as "Chip".

For someone with no family he easily took to the cause of the Flufuza who showed him a dream of a prosperous future. Little did Chip know that he took to the dark side.  

As the Flufza grew in power Chip enjoyed luxuries he could only imagine. Flufuza was becoming strong and threatening peace of the Fluffle. The elders of the Fluffle did everything to prevent the Flufuza from taking over the 'Great Tree' but the Flufuza was willing to go to war and wipe out the Fluffle if they had to. The Fluffle elders had no choice. But they were afraid the end was near  for the Fluffle, for war would destroy them all.

'Chip' only wanted a life of luxury. He had already lost 2 parents in 'the wreck' and didn't want to lose his Fluffle. Spying on the Flufuza heads he leaked their war plans to Fluffle elders. The elders with their commanders spoilt the Flufuza's plans and avoided the war. Flufuza's were banished from the underground. Chip was honored and was offered a place in high society for his efforts to save the Fluffle. But Chip refused for he realised that wealth and greed benefits no one. He chose to remain a free spirit. 

The banished Flufuza joined with humankind and still threatened peace of the Fluffle which eventually led to 'The Hibernation'. (But that is story for another day)

When a few Fluf's came out of Hibernation, Chip was one of the chosen few. You can still find him roaming in the Fluf avenue markets, making sure that other young Fluf's like him with no family are lured by the evil.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

Watch this space!!

name: Rebel Rabbit
description: This girl knows she is the queen of the neighborhood, having grown up in the original Riot Rabbbbiiit movement of the early 90s our own Rebel Rabbit is a tad more chilled nowadays.  Her penchant for the Rabbit Rebellion all those years ago, has not taken a toll, but it has given her experience.  With many Bunnies growing up without the knowledge of her great past, Rebel delivers MUCx -Metaverse, Underground, Carrots, talks around the Underground for groups interested to hear about how she has fought for Rabbit equality and Rabbit prosperity.  Her personal launch into FLUFfi has seen her own wealth grow and she is very comfortable.  When not doing MUCx talks she is developing new financial products for the Underground, to help other Flufs into FLUFfi.  Her focus has been on simple onboarding and encouraging the use of Carrotcoin investments.  Representing Lagomorphs Against Chocolate Easter Rabbits, aka LACER in her spare time, something she kicked off after seeing a Human eating the ears off a chocolate rabbit in a supermarket car park, Rebel is constantly busy.  When she has time to relax you will find her at her Tiki bar on the coast.  Not with a freshly extracted carrot juice, that would be a cliche, she prefers a Gin and Coke Zero Sugar with a fresh lime.  I said not a cliche, not that she has taste.

name: Whispering Pixie
description: Hi, Im Pixie the animal whisperer. My parents were farmers back before the wreck and grew all your most favourite fruit and vegetables for all of fluf world.  Did you know that animals, including insects and fish, are all vital parts for sustaining the environment and food chain? Well, my parents were pure bred mystics with hypnotic eyes and pa ssed on the ability to me to be able to communicate with most living things, in a subtle special way, including plants to some degree. When we farmed, our abilities helped us ask help from animals for everything from plowing grounds for carrots to carrying loads of carrots, to asking bees to pollinate and asking birds not to attack, and asking when the plants were ready for harvest. So anyway, after the wreck we lost our lands and everything was new, the great reset some call it. And living in this coastal environment I have taken up diving as well and love communicating with fish, dolphins, and other species. You can often see me training animals, picking daisies and making daisy chain crowns, and just generally being connected with flora and fauna. As Im sure youre aware, most mystics enjoy a little extra mycelium to maintain their powers, that definitely keeps me connected, and regular micro doses enhances my special abilities. Luckily the community gives us extra rations if they think we deserve it. I often find animals and plants easier to get on with than some fluf. Although Zombie fluf are an interesting one. Some of them tend to be quite aggressive, perhaps resentful that they caught the disease, its hard to communicate with them, but I can sense something brewing in whats left of their brains. Our hypnotic eyes are the most peaceful way to deal with troubles with Zombies, just like wild animals. I always have my trusty high pitch sonic whistle when things go wrong. Hopefully you dont have to hear that. Ive rambled enough, thanks for listening. Please come watch me training my animal friends and maybe I can help you feel more connected too.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.
